item.title: Fishes in the Tank and the Ocean
Won $100 :)
item.description: Food On Wednesday March 8, I arrived, for the first time, at Mo-mo paradise in Mira Mesa with Alan and Eric for all-you-can-eat shabu-shabu and sukiyaki. We all got very full and enjoyed the meal. Right after, we decided to go to the Meet Fresh that is also in Mira Mesa. Since Eric and I have to get back to campus for a contest in time, we ran to the bus station and took the bus to the Meet Fresh.
